WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:01.611
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:01.611 --> 00:00:03.211
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.211 --> 00:00:04.354
Well, praise the Lord.

00:00:04.354 --> 00:00:06.440
I really appreciate you joining me.

00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:24.900
I was sent some articles about what I saw regarding the cyber attacks, and people are sending me stuff saying, 'Brandon, we started looking into what you were talking about and the United States is using Windows 95 with the FAA.

00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:28.293
' And I was like, 'Surely not.

00:00:28.293 --> 00:00:29.406
' 30-year-old software.

00:00:29.406 --> 00:00:30.777
Like, really?

00:00:30.777 --> 00:00:39.680
I mean, so Braden started researching and making sure before I talk about it, you know, because you don't want to look off.

00:00:40.060 --> 00:00:41.771
You want to make sure it's right.

00:00:41.771 --> 00:01:01.199
They are using 1995 floppy disks, and they're trying to update it, and they're saying it's going to take at least four years because of how vast this system is and all the computers, and it's going to cost billions of dollars to renew the infrastructure of the FAA computer systems.

00:01:01.199 --> 00:01:03.485
Billions is what they're saying.

00:01:03.485 --> 00:01:09.376
So all that I was talking about and what the Lord showed me in my prayer time is legit.

00:01:09.376 --> 00:01:19.268
Obviously, when you're using software from 1995, and it's 30-year-old software, and you're using computers with floppy disks, I mean, this is a major deal.

00:01:19.268 --> 00:01:31.314
We're going into a new industrial revolution with 1995 software, with AI technology using quantum computers, and we have 1995 software with AI.

00:01:31.314 --> 00:01:41.451
So obviously, when you have other countries being able to tap into the AI and hack into our infrastructure, it's probably not going to be that hard.

00:01:42.183 --> 00:01:44.729
I wonder if they're using dial-up, you know?

00:01:44.729 --> 00:01:50.000
I mean, and it's like, no, this is not cool.

00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:57.680
And they're saying it could take up to four years, so that's all of President Trump's term, clear up past it.

00:01:57.680 --> 00:02:00.491
I mean, that's a major deal.

00:02:00.491 --> 00:02:02.999
So, that was part of it.

00:02:02.999 --> 00:02:09.679
Then, right after that, we see the airlines that the Lord spoke to me about.

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:12.926
One was on fire and had to do an emergency landing in the middle of the air.

00:02:12.926 --> 00:02:16.480
This is another sign of something that the Lord's trying to warn everybody about.

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:28.228
Right after I give you the word, not even 24 hours later, there's a plane and it's caught fire in the middle of the air, and it has to do an emergency landing, and you can see people filming it and it's burning and doing all this stuff.

00:02:28.228 --> 00:02:32.200
And I thought, 'Lord, you're speaking so loud trying to warn your people to pray.

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:36.789
' You know, like I said, God has not called us to fear; He has called us to pray.

00:02:36.789 --> 00:02:42.319
But He's warning us about things, telling us, 'Look, look, look, there's a problem here.

00:02:42.319 --> 00:02:43.360
There's a problem there.

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:48.542
' And when I saw the plane falling out of the sky, you know, I don't know what caused that.

00:02:48.542 --> 00:02:54.120
I was assuming cyber attacks, but how could you get to the plane and turn it off?

00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:55.320
I have no idea.

00:02:55.320 --> 00:03:02.479
All I know is I saw a plane; its dash went completely blank and it fell, and it was very dangerous.

00:03:03.386 --> 00:03:05.049
I could tell you where it was leaving from.

00:03:05.049 --> 00:03:12.139
It was leaving from the central part of America and it was going northeast.

00:03:12.139 --> 00:03:18.871
It was going northeast to like the Boston area, and this was a major flight, and it was halfway there and it went down.

00:03:18.871 --> 00:03:20.926
I can tell you that's what it looked like.

00:03:21.330 --> 00:03:23.067
Now, is that going to be every plane?

00:03:23.067 --> 00:03:29.817
And is that just something that the Lord's trying to show us, is what I'm trying to say, or is that the exact flight?

00:03:30.992 --> 00:03:37.074
Because sometimes He's just showing me an example of something to pray about and saying, 'Hey, just letting you know the flights.

00:03:37.074 --> 00:03:42.640
' Just kind of like people are saying about the boat, and they're trying to figure out, and they have trackers on all the boats.

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:52.217
So, you're sending me the trackers of all the red decks with all the black-bottom boats with the white thing, and they're sending stuff, saying 'we got to track this boat, and this is where it's at.

00:03:52.217 --> 00:03:58.710
' Now folks, I'm going to tell you, whenever I saw this boat, it was leaving Africa.

00:03:58.710 --> 00:04:04.818
It was leaving that area over there, and it was headed this way.

00:04:04.818 --> 00:04:07.999
So, the crew—I've told you all about that.

00:04:07.999 --> 00:04:13.680
I don't need to rehearse all that, but it was coming out of the Europe area, Africa, all that area.

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:18.868
That's all I remember—seeing Africa in a distance, and it was coming out of that area.

00:04:19.256 --> 00:04:29.555
And number three, about what people wanted to know about the buildings and the electric outages: I saw cyber attacks coming upon our electric grid, that it was very vulnerable.

00:04:29.555 --> 00:04:36.559
And I saw it was a major city, and I saw it was New York, and it was completely dark.

00:04:36.559 --> 00:04:47.991
And that's whenever I told my son they were trying to bring in generators to keep people from looting and rioting, stealing everything because it was so dark in the city.

00:04:47.991 --> 00:05:00.719
And I could remember seeing those big spotlights running on generators, trying to keep sections of the city lit up so that the police and the law enforcement could keep law and order in that area when the electricity was off.

00:05:00.719 --> 00:05:03.600
But I remember it was very hot outside.

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:07.199
And I told Braden, I even saw the emergency power on hospitals coming on.

00:05:08.056 --> 00:05:17.839
So they were trying to keep people alive in hospitals, but it was a dimmer light; it wasn't as bright as normal, like the hospital all lit up—it was like backup power.

00:05:17.839 --> 00:05:32.924
And so, you know, I see these things, but I thought it was interesting in this vision, whenever I was praying and the Lord was showing me that the light was shining on the buildings, trying to cause a mirror effect so that it would glow more instead of just having it shoot straight up in the air.

00:05:32.924 --> 00:05:40.663
It was trying to shine on the buildings to cause light down below, like blocking the light from just going straight up is what it would look like in the vision.

00:05:40.663 --> 00:05:42.764
So, that's part of what I saw too.

00:05:42.764 --> 00:05:47.310
So, you know, I see all these things and the Lord tells us what to pray about.

00:05:48.096 --> 00:05:56.840
I believe there's a lot of things that we can stop in prayer, as everybody knows who is a prayer warrior.

00:05:56.840 --> 00:06:06.249
Hey, and by the way, whoever sent me these hankies because I was using the Kleenex there, she embroidered my last name on it.

00:06:06.249 --> 00:06:09.333
And I thought it was really nice of the sister to do that.

00:06:09.333 --> 00:06:12.364
You know, it's too pretty to blow your nose in.

00:06:12.364 --> 00:06:14.773
I was like, 'Hey, you know, somebody writes your name on it.

00:06:14.773 --> 00:06:17.340
' I don't blow my nose in it, but it's really pretty.

00:06:17.340 --> 00:06:18.240
I appreciate it.

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:21.084
You know, that people take the time to do stuff like that.

00:06:21.084 --> 00:06:24.537
I don't know if you had a machine do that or whatever, but I thought it was kind of cool.

00:06:24.537 --> 00:06:30.460
The other thing: praying over our water supply, praying over because, you know, I've told you about the water supply.

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:55.097
